    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 3200, 4100, 4200, 4300, 4400, 7300, 7400, 7500, 7600, 8500, 8600
        Models Built After 05/19/2003 - CAB FEATURES - LIGHTED AIR SHIELD - EXTENDED DESCRIPTION
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>EXTENDED DESCRIPTION</title>
        <para>When park lights or headlights are requested, the ESC will supply ground to the coil of lighted air shield
            relay.
        </para>
        <para>This will cause the relay to energize, supplying power to the air shield light.</para>
    </svcproc>
